,98,270,20,512,31],"class_list":["post-36229","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-faith-iman","tag-congregational-prayer-salat-jamaah","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-ostentation-al-riya","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-recommendation-al-mustahab","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9ql","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14752,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/28\/salat-no-voluntary-obligatory\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer when obligatory prayer begins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the prayer commences, there is no prayer but the prescribed prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 710 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Tirmidhi said, \"This was acted upon by some of the people of knowledge among the companions\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5514,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/25\/virtue-salat-first-row-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Virtue of praying in first row of congregation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubay ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the first row of prayer resembles the rows of angels. If you knew its virtue, you would compete for it. The prayer of a man with another man is more purifying than his prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25718,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/09\/salat-jamaah-already-prayed\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jama&#8217;ah: Pray with congregation, even if already prayed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Al-Aswad reported: I witness the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I prayed the dawn prayer with him in the mosque of Al-Khaif. When the Prophet finished his prayer and turned around, he saw two men in the back of the people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36227,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/21\/nafl-better-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers better at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayb ibn al-Nu\u2019man reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe voluntary prayer of a man in his house is better than his prayer where people can see him, just as the prescribed prayers are better than the voluntary prayers.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 7322\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7645,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/best-nalf-salat-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Best voluntary prayer offered at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"O people, perform prayer in your houses, for the best prayer of a man is in his house, except for the prescribed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 731 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-between-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36229,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Continuous praying between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I performed the evening prayer with him. The Prophet continued to pray until the evening prayer. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635